task.summary: Renamed protocol to protocolOf for clarity.
Added .idea to .gitignore and incremented version number
Protocols are now resolved as an instance of their own class.
Added ProtocolSpecification so protocols can be shared
Documented PolymorphicDeserializer and updated serialized composite types in companion of StaticDeserializer.
Polymorphic write test is now passing.
Added Dokka packages and generated test binaries
Added proper variances to type parameters in Operations.kt.
Added fallback and static to local protocol test.
Simplified API. Some bugfixes and performance improvements. Updated README.md.
